This is my attempt to create a Pokédex out of Pokémon cards. <!-- https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/User:Maverick_Nate/Illustrators -->

## Conditions

- The Pokémon should not have a Rule Box. (Sorry, Eternatus, but it's kind of forced for you.)
- The card may still be a Full Art card.
- No two illustrators are to illustrate a card of a Pokémon from the same generation.
  - BTW, tetsuya koizumi and Scav are the same person.
    - Kazuma Koda might be already doing artwork under the name Lownine, but no cards in the TCG credit them as Lownine.
- Regional forms are treated as a Pokémon from the generation the *form* debuted in.
- State as of Stellar Crown.

